
Expand common Journal abbreviations if they are unrecognized. These commands
will expand various control sequences such as

   \apj     ---> Astrophys. J.
   \nat     ---> Nature
   \grl     ---> Geophys. Res. Lett.
   \icarus  ---> Icarus
   \aap     ---> Astron. Astrophys.
   \physscr ---> Phys. Scripta
   \ssr     ---> Space Sci. Rev.
   \pre     ---> Phys. Rev. E

